ğŸŸ¦ Conclusion

This project successfully demonstrates a multifunctional robotic system capable of both autonomous obstacle avoidance and manual wireless control. The combination of an ultrasonic sensor, servo motor, and Bluetooth communication provides enhanced interactivity and intelligent decision-making.

The robot effectively showcases essential robotics concepts such as sensor fusion, real-time control, motor driving, and wireless communication.
It is an excellent academic project that forms a strong foundation for future enhancements like IoT control, AI navigation, or camera-based monitoring.
